---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Leadership · VAI"
  description="Veterinary Academy International was established under the veterinary leadership of Dr. Soheyl Simaei and is being developed with experienced veterinary professionals and educators."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Leadership"
    title="Founder-led. Academically collaborative."
    lede="Veterinary Academy International was established under experienced veterinary leadership and is being developed in collaboration with veterinary professionals, educators, and subject-matter experts."
  />

  <Section>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 md:gap-14 items-start max-w-5xl">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <figure class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden bg-platinum-soft">
            <img
              src="/founder-portrait.png"
              alt="Dr. Soheyl Simaei, Founder & Academic Director of Veterinary Academy International"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="block w-full h-full object-cover"
              style="object-position: 50% 20%;"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-px left-0 w-12 h-px bg-champagne"></div>
        </figure>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <div class="font-serif text-xl text-navy-deep">Dr. Soheyl Simaei</div>
          <div class="eyebrow mt-2">Founder &amp; Academic Director</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 prose-editorial">
        <p>Veterinary Academy International was established under the leadership of <strong class="text-navy-deep font-medium">Dr. Soheyl Simaei</strong>, a veterinarian and educator with more than two decades of clinical, leadership, and entrepreneurial experience.</p>
        <p>Before establishing VAI, Dr. Simaei spent more than two decades in veterinary practice, clinical leadership, and veterinary entrepreneurship, building and leading a respected veterinary business in Dubai. This experience now informs his work in postgraduate veterinary education, professional development, and clinical leadership training.</p>
        <p>VAI is being developed in collaboration with experienced veterinary professionals, educators, and subject-matter experts. Faculty announcements will be made as programmes mature.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Parent Institution" title="A specialised academy of Academia Europa." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-5xl">
      <p>VAI is the first specialised academy of <a href="https://academiaeuropa.com" rel="noopener" class="text-navy-deep underline decoration-champagne underline-offset-4">Academia Europa</a>, a European institution for postgraduate professional education. Academia Europa is operated by Solex Education Unipessoal LDA, Portugal.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Base>
